27 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 26-57-203, concerning definitions within
28 the Arkansas Tobacco Products Tax Act of 1977, is amended to add additional
29 subdivisions to read as follows:
30 (38) "Disposable vapor product" means a vapor product that:
31 (A) Has a battery that is not detachable from the atomizer
32 or vaporizer;
33 (B) Cannot be refilled with e-liquid; and
34 (C) Is designed to be disposed of after the e-liquid is
35 used; and
36 (39) “Prohibited foreign party” means the same as in § 18-11-802.
