19 SECTION 3. DO NOT CODIFY. TEMPORARY LANGUAGE. Notice of act
20 requirements and allowance of a grace period.
21 The Director of Arkansas Tobacco Control shall notify manufacturers,
22 wholesalers, retailers, and vendors licensed under § 26-57-219 of:
23 (1) The requirements of this act and the time frame in which
24 compliance is required; and
25 (2) The allowance of a ninety-day grace period following the
26 effective date of this act during which any disposal vapor product from a
27 prohibited foreign party in their possession shall be liquidated, sold, or
28 disposed of.
